ABOUT

This is a website made for all of you that are interested in space. Here you can keep track of SpaceX`s rockets and launches.

SpaceX is a private American aerospace manufacturer and space transportation services company headquartered in Hawthorne, California.

SpaceX is founded by Elon Musk.
Elon Musk is an engineer, industrial designer, technology entrepreneur, and philanthropist (meaning, a desire to promote the welfare of others by generous donations of money to good causes.).

This website is created with an Open Source Rest API https://docs.spacexdata.com
